page.title: 08MY DOG, JENNY FOX
page.content: My dog is very good for training. She does as she is told. She is good for her age. She is only a puppy and is six months old. Her name is Jenny Fox. My family is called Fox. {House training She is very good in the house. She does not go to the toilet in the house but does play around with the cats. {Safety training We have taught Jenny not to cross the road until she has sat down at the kerb. Now when we take her to the field she sits at the kerb straight away. { Other training We have taught Jenny to fetch the ball and give the ball. She is very good at doing things when she is told. { Behaviour Jenny is very good. But she does chew a lot of things.
